--------------- user upload ---------------
// User selects file -> GeneratorPage updates imageSrc state 
// -> handleGenerate processes it.

ImageUpload -> PaletteGenerator -> ColorExtractor
--------------- --------------- ---------------


--------------- random image ---------------
// User clicks "Random" -> api.js fetches URL 
// -> GeneratorPage sets imageSrc -> handleGenerate processes it.

PaletteGenerator -> API -> ColorExtractor
--------------- --------------- ---------------


--------------- display results ---------------
// GeneratorPage calls setPalette (Lifting State) 
// -> PaletteDisplay receives new palette prop -> Renders colors.

PaletteGenerator -> PaletteDisplay -> ColorSquare
--------------- --------------- ---------------


